# How to domesticate Eclipse IDE

## show heap status (RAM usage)
* go to Window>Preferences
* on the right side (under General) tick "Show heap status"

## turning on dark mode

* go to Window>Preferences>
* tick on "Enable theming"
* choose Dark theme of your choice
* Apply & Close
* Restart Eclipse

## install Git

* Go to Help>Install new Software>
* select Work with: --All Available Sites--
* type filter text: git
* select packages you need, e.g. "Git integration for Eclipse"
* next ...

